Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是高盧的首都律特斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是塔帕莎的故鄉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在飛艇修理完畢前 能麻煩妳一段時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還能看到其他的蠻人國家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是被研究之神護佑著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算賭氣硬來我也該跟著比達夏爾卿走的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別像那樣哀聲嘆氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是新婚旅行嘛 好好享受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才人真是的 跑哪裡去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 你們兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法說沒有這個的話會很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 「蒂法 蒂法」的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先成為你的主人的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是蒂法的對手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就妳這身洗衣板真虧能贏得了她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才人他喜歡貧乳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你摸她胸部的時候不是挺開心的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(434,435)\fs30}什麼啊 我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好繼位加冕的準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.81,0:01:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來她下定決心了呢

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,—————————————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:56.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.28,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽ばたいて行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:05.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい世界へ GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手と手を繋いで進めば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:16.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇さえ恐れず行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:21.92,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰もまだ知らないあの場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中で嵐に遭っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:28.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見守る瞳の灯りが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:32.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち向かう勇気をくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:38.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法より強い力さ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:44.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かけがえのない君を思う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:49.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この場 ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.02,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:03:01.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂しさも唇も強気な眼差しも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.24,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好きさ ALWAYS I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らなら出来る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:12.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷ついて 乗り越えて 心から笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:19.25,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい世界へ GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:56.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.28,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飛出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:05.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著嶄新的世界 GO WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要手牽手一起前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:16.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連黑暗也無足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:21.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著未曾有人知曉的那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算途中遭遇暴風雨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:28.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你守望的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:32.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予了我奮勇抗爭的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:38.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是比魔法更強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:44.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心懷無可替代的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:49.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立於此地 ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 I'LL BE THERE FOR YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你我之間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:03:01.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的寂寞 你的嘴唇 你的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.24,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都喜歡喔  ALWAYS I LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:06.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的話一定可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:12.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路受傷一路克服 發自真心的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:19.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著嶄新的世界 GO WITH ME
